# GitHub Backend Assignment

# Host Lik :https://github-followers-nu.vercel.app/
# Github Link : https://github.com/aadil-nv/Github-followers

A full-stack project with a **Node.js + Express + TypeScript backend** and a **Vite + React frontend**.  
The backend integrates with the GitHub API to fetch, store, and manage user details, while the frontend provides a simple UI to search and explore GitHub followers.  

---

## 🚀 Features
- Save GitHub user details to database (avoid duplicate API calls)  
- Find mutual followers (friends)  
- Search users by username, location, etc.  
- Soft delete user records  
- Update user profile fields (bio, blog, location, etc.)  
- List users sorted by followers, repos, etc.  
- Input validation & error handling  
- Repository-based architecture  
- Unit & Integration tests with Jest  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Node.js, Express, TypeScript, TypeORM, Axios  
- **Frontend**: Vite, React, Tailwind CSS  
- **Database**: SQLite / PostgreSQL  
- **Testing**: Jest, Supertest  

---

## ▶️ Getting Started

### 🔹 Backend
```bash
cd backend
npm install
npm start


### 🔹 frontend

cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev

